name: SuperScar
description:
My very first body painting on model, SCAR, back in 2010, one of my all time favorite models. I wanted to take advantage of the disappearing phone booths in the neighborhood. This one was a block away from the police station, but we managed to shoot there for around 45 minutes without trouble.

model: Scar
body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
